public class PopupCategorized extends Object implements PopupExtension.PopupMenuBuilder, Cloneable
a menu builder for categorizing items. 
     [ labelItem1 //PopupCategorized.CategorizedMenuItemLabel,
       labelItem2,
       ...
      category1,
      [item1_1: icon, name],
      [item1_2  ... ],
      ...
      category2,
      item2_1,
      item2_2,
      ...,
      ]
